# desktop/ frontend configuration. Copy to `.env` and adjust. Vite only exposes
# vars prefixed VITE_ to client code.

# Backend WebSocket origin. HTTP calls derive from this (ws:// -> http://). The
# Nostr-shaped community/invite features also read this, though they have no
# backend counterpart yet.
#
# The Tauri dev server runs on :1420 (see vite.config.ts), so the backend's CORS
# origin must be overridden to match — run the backend with
# GEAR6_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:1420, otherwise rtm.connect is blocked.
VITE_RELAY_URL=ws://localhost:3000
